#  Control → NIS 2 Article Mapping (Directive (EU) 2022/2555)
 Source of legal text: EUR-Lex (CELEX:32022L2555). Store article-by-article
 excerpts under each control’s “NIS 2/NIST Contextual Notes”.
 URL: https://eur-lex.europa.eu/legal-content/EN/TXT/?uri=CELEX:32022L2555
