Function: PROTECT (PR)
 Category: Identity Management, Authentication and Access Control (PR.AC): Access to
 physical and logical assets and associated facilities is limited to authorized users, processes,
 and devices, and is managed consistent with the assessed risk of unauthorized access to
 authorized activities and transactions.
 Key Measure: Key Measure
 Requirement: PR.AC-4.4: Nobody shall have administrator privileges for daily tasks.
 Guidance: Consider the following:
 â€¢ Separate administrator accounts from user accounts.
 â€¢ Donotprivilege user accounts to effectuate administration tasks.
 â€¢ Create unique local administrator passwords and disable unused accounts.
 â€¢ Consider prohibiting Internet browsing from administrative accounts.
