related duties and responsibilities consistent with related policies, procedures, and agreements.
 Subcategory: PR.DS-3: Assets are formally managed throughout removal, transfers, and
 disposition
 Requirement: PR.DS-3.1: Assets and media shall be disposed of safely.
 Guidance: â€¢
 When eliminating tangible assets like business computers/laptops,
 servers, hard drive(s) and other storage media (USB drives, paperâ€¦), ensure that all
 sensitive business or personal data are securely deleted (i.e. electronically â€œwipedâ€ )
 before they are removed and then physically destroyed (or re-commissioned). This is also
 known as â€œsanitizationâ€ and thus related to the requirement and guidance in PR.IP-6.
 â€¢
 Consider installing a remote-wiping application on company laptops, tablets, cell phones,
 and other mobile devices.
