Function: PROTECT (PR)
 Category: Maintenance (PR.MA): Maintenance and repairs of industrial control and information
 system components are performed consistent with policies and procedures.
 Key Measure: Key Measure
 Subcategory: PR.MA-1: Maintenance and repair of organizational assets are performed and
 logged, with approved and controlled tools
 Requirement: PR.MA-1.1: Patches and security updates for Operating Systems and critical
 system components shall be installed.
 Guidance: The following should be considered:
 â€¢ Limit yourself to only install those applications (operating systems, firmware, or plugins )
 that you need to run your business and patch/update them regularly.
 â€¢ Youshould only install a current and vendor-supported version of software you choose
 to use. It may be useful to assign a day each month to check for patches.
 â€¢ Thereare products which can scan your system and notify you when there is an update
 for an application you have installed. If you use one of these products, make sure it checks for
 updates for every application you use.
 â€¢ Install patches and security updates in a timely manner.
