 CyberFundamentals Maturity Level BASIC (Radar
 Summary)
 Purpose:
 This radar visualization provides a comparative view of the organization’s maturity levels across
 all CyberFundamentals categories.
 Axes represent:
 · EachCyberFundamentals category (IDENTIFY, PROTECT, DETECT, RESPOND,
 RECOVER).
 · Maturity levels ranging from 0 to 5, with:
 o 5=Optimizing
 o 4=Managed
 o 3=Defined
 o 2=Repeatable
 o 1=Initial
 o 0=Non-existent
 Plotted Data:
· Greenline: Target Maturity Score
 · Orangeline: Category Maturity Score
 · Greyline: Documentation Maturity Score
 · Blueline: Implementation Maturity Score
