 shall be monitored for unauthorized personnel access, connections,
 devices, access points, and software.
 Guidance: • Unauthorized personnel access includes access by
 external service providers.
 • System inventory discrepancies should be included in the
 monitoring.
 • Unauthorized configuration changes to organization's critical
 systems should be included in the monitoring.
