Function: RESPOND (RS)
 Category: Analysis (RS.AN): Analysis is conducted to ensure effective
 response and support recovery activities.
 Key Measure: Key Measure
 Subcategory: RS.AN-5: Processes are established to receive, analyze
 and respond to vulnerabilities disclosed to the organization from
 internal and external sources (e.g. internal testing, security
 bulletins, or security researchers)
 Requirement: RS.AN-5.1: The organization shall implement vulnerability
 management processes and procedures that include processing, analyzing
 and remedying vulnerabilities from internal and external sources.
 Guidance: Internal and external sources could be e.g. internal
 testing, security bulletins, or security researchers.
