 organization’s risk strategy.
 Requirement: ID.AM-4.2: The flow of information to/from external
 systems shall be mapped, documented, authorized, and update when
 changes occur.
 Guidance: Consider requiring external service providers to identify
 and document the functions, ports, protocols, and services necessary
 for the connection services.
