 Key Measure: Key Measure
 Requirement: BASIC_PR.AC-3.2: The organization's networks when
 accessed remotely shall be secured, including through multi-factor
 authentication (MFA).
 Guidance: Enforce MFA (e.g. 2FA) on Internet-facing systems, such as
 email, remote desktop, and Virtual Private Network (VPNs).
