 the confidentiality, integrity, and availability of information.
 Requirement: PR.DS-3.4: The organization shall ensure that disposal
 actions are approved, tracked, documented, and verified.
 Guidance: Disposal actions include media sanitization actions (See
 PR.IP-6)
