organizational entities), processes, and procedures are maintained and
 used to manage protection of information systems and assets.
 Requirement: PR.IP-4.5: Critical system backup shall be separated from
 critical information backup.
 Guidance: Seperation of critical system backup from critical
 information backup should lead to a shorter recovery time.
