 organizational entities), processes, and procedures are maintained and
 used to manage protection of information systems and assets.
Requirement: PR.IP-6.2: Sanitation processes shall be documented and
 tested.
 Guidance: • Sanitation processes include procedures and equipment.
 • Consider applying non-destructive sanitization techniques to
 portable storage devices.
 • Consider sanitation procedures in proportion to confidentiality
 requirements.
