 Subcategory: RS.AN-4: Incidents are categorized consistent with
 response plans
 Requirement: IMPORTANT_RS.AN-4.1: Information/cybersecurity incidents
 shall be categorized according to the level of severity and impact
 consistent with the evaluation criteria included the incident response
 plan.
 Guidance: • It should be considered to determine the causes of an
 information/cybersecurity incident and implement a corrective action
 in order that the incident does not recur or occur elsewhere.
 • The effectiveness of any corrective action taken should be
 reviewed.
 • Corrective actions should be appropriate to the effects of the
 information/cybersecurity incident encountered.
