Requirement: IMPORTANT_RS.AN-5.1: The organization shall implement
 vulnerability management processes and procedures that include
 processing, analyzing and remedying vulnerabilities from internal and
 external sources.
 Guidance: Internal and external sources could be e.g. internal
 testing, security bulletins, or security researchers.
