 KMMaturity Score: 1.00
 Documentation Maturity Score: 1.00
 Implementation Maturity Score: 1.00
 · PR.IP-4.1 —Backups for organization’s business critical data shall be conducted and
 stored on a system different from the device on which the original data resides.
