 segregation.
 PR.AC-5.2 — Where appropriate, network integrity of the organization’s
 critical systems shall be protected by incorporating network segmentation and
 segregation.
 PR.AC-5.3 — Where appropriate, network integrity of the organization’s
 critical systems shall be protected by:
 PR.AC-5.3 — Where appropriate, network integrity of the organization’s
 critical systems shall be protected by:
 PR.AC-5.4 — The organization shall monitor and control connections and
 communications at the external boundary and at key internal boundaries within
 the organization’s critical systems by implementing boundary protection
 devices where appropriate.
 PR.AC-5.4 — The organization shall monitor and control connections and
